```plantuml
@startuml IBM_vpc-flowlogs-log-analysis
actor User
participant "IBM Cloud Functions" as ICF
participant "COS Trigger" as COSTrigger
participant "COS Bucket (Receiver)" as COSReceiver
participant "handler.js" as Handler
participant "IBM Log Analysis API" as LogAnalysis
participant "COS Bucket (Archive)" as COSArchive

User -> ICF: Deploy Function
ICF -> COSTrigger: Configure COS Trigger
COSTrigger -> ICF: Monitor COS Bucket

loop On New Log File
    COSReceiver -> COSTrigger: Object Created Event
    COSTrigger -> Handler: Invoke Function (event)
    
    Handler -> COSReceiver: Get Object (log file)
    COSReceiver --> Handler: Return compressed log
    
    Handler -> Handler: Decompress log
    Handler -> Handler: Parse JSON
    Handler -> Handler: Transform Data
    
    alt Forward to Log Analysis
        Handler -> LogAnalysis: Send Logs (API Call)
        LogAnalysis --> Handler: Response
    end
    
    Handler -> COSArchive: Copy to Archive
    Handler -> COSReceiver: Delete Original
    
    Handler --> ICF: Processing Complete
end
@enduml
```